{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we saw these bombers going over-- I think it was bombers anyhow-- and all of a sudden, this one guy made a circle and came back and dropped about four or five bombs down there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We found out after the war that he had a problem down there and dropped it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the SS men were terrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They started to mingle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took off their cap, and they started to mingle with us, because we had striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was like a sea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As if the guy would see it from that far up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the irony of the whole thing is that, after the war, when I worked for the CIC, I got drunk every night.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had sex 16 times a night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, that's bragging, but I had a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I enjoy-- I wanted to have life back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I looked for these guys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met a colonel from the Air Force, and we both got drunk-- roaring drunk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were talking about this, and he told me where he went, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to him one day, I said, you know, there's one thing-- why didn't that goddamn Air Force bomb Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you guys know about it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, you know, from what I've just learned-- not this moment, but before that-- is that you had to go over Auschwitz to get to Ploiesti.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ploiesti was in Romania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the oil fields were down there that you bombed out of Italy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he said, I know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I did that, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, so why didn't you drop a bomb and knock out at least the crematorias?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, he said, well, you know, we were told that we would kill prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
